def find_uncle_johny_position(test_cases):
    positions = []
    for case in test_cases:
        N = case['N']
        A = case['A']
        K = case['K']
        uncle_johny_length = A[K - 1]
        sorted_A = sorted(A)
        new_position = sorted_A.index(uncle_johny_length) - 1
        positions.append(new_position)
    return positions
